[g]Planned Improvements[/g]

A list of planned improvements will be kept in this thread so that the [g]Con(phi)[/g][g_]d[/g_] community is able to know what new features will soon be available to them.

[m](b2)[/m] Alternate colour scheme for those who prefer reading black on white.
[m](b2)[/m] If required, some kind of method for blacklisting certain users or IP addresses from certain threads.
[m](b2)[/m] Private message system (plans exist for a simple thread-based solution).
[m](b2)[/m] Ability to link images to posts.
